title: Looney Tunes Roadrunner Best of Vol 1-Greek/English audio
description:
This Golden Era collection captures Road Runner and his pals where it matters most - uncut and on tape in some of the craziest characters ever to strap themselves to an Acme Rocket. You never know what Wile E. Coyote will try next. But you know he'll try, using a huge slingshot, a dehydrated boulder (just add water!) tornado seeds and other Acme gizmos of feverish design. The chase is on. So is the fun. Beep beep!!

English and Greek audio.Greek subtitles.

Thanks to aristotelisfot
